schools.name: Lake Balboa College Preparatory Magnet K-12

data.description: This single level remodeled residence is set behind impressive gates on an expansive lot of landscaped parklike grounds with a stunning towering cedar tree that greets as you enter the gated double entry motor court to a sweeping grass filled front yard that sets the tone for this magical property. Set far back from the street, a unique covered front patio with skylights and ceilings fans is the perfect backdrop to enjoy the beautiful grounds and creates a special entry into this unique home. Porcelain tile, hardwood flooring and high ceilings throughout converge as you enter the great room that leads to the dining area and a chef’s gourmet-styled kitchen with customized dark wood cabinets, granite counter tops, glass tiled backsplash and a center island with seating and storage. All secondary bedrooms are ensuite with ceiling fans and walk-in closets, the perfect complement to the primary suite that features an alcove area perfect for an office, a walk-in closet behind frosted glass wood framed doors and a 2-person shower with dual shower heads and dual sinks. The direct access oversized 2-car garage also contains entry into an ensuite bonus room. A built-in Spanish tiled grill station overlooks lush green grassy areas filled with lemon and orange trees and a garden growing tomatoes, bell peppers, watermelon, and cantaloupe. Additional amenities include designer fixtures, recessed lighting, crown moldings, indoor laundry, and gated parking galore at the front and rear of the property. Close to restaurants, shopping, and all the valley has to offer. Truly a must see!
